15. Conclusion

Cloud Computing has transformed the way organizations deploy and manage IT resources. By providing scalable, flexible, and cost-effective solutions, cloud technologies enable businesses and individuals to innovate faster and operate more efficiently. Understanding cloud computing concepts is essential for modern software development, IT infrastructure management, and digital transformation.

